"""
    Test of arc_error()
    """
expected_vals = np.array([30.19765553, -1.40779391, 14.19212336])
a = 1.3
b = 2.2
c = 0.5
abc_vals = a, b, c
first_point = 30.2
coef1 = 0.05995294
coef2 = -4.086e-05
coef3 = -5.21e-06
abil_deprec = 0.47
params = first_point, coef1, coef2, coef3, abil_deprec
test_vals = income.arc_error(abc_vals, params)
assert np.allclose(test_vals, expected_vals)
